{rbtgr_build_json}
.. {rbbc_require}
HTTP 200 response
.. {rbbc_store}
`«BUILD_ID»` from response `.metadata.build.id`
.. {rbbc_show}
build dispatched with `«BUILD_ID»`
.. {rbbc_show}
Cloud Console URL for build monitoring

//axhos_step
. *Cloud Build Execution*:
.. NOTE: Build executes via OCI Layout Bridge pattern to solve BuildKit credential isolation. See Trade Study RBSOB for design rationale.
.. {gcb_service}
executes the following phases within the
{rbtgi_depot_project}:
... *Build Phase*: Multi-platform container compilation produces OCI Image Layout artifact in shared workspace. No registry credentials required.
... *Push Phase*: OCI artifact copied to
{rbtgi_repository}
using
{oauth_token}
obtained from
{gcb_service}
metadata server.
